{"title":"搭建简易QQ机器人","uid":"17f86a1e230b959f5e656d2cbd6d894d","slug":"搭建简易QQ机器人","date":"2023-05-24T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2023-05-24T13:00:00.078Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/搭建简易QQ机器人.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img4.a0bi.com/upload/articleResource/20230407/1680850578475.png","content":"<p>之前有个一次性需要通知很多人的需求，而那些需要通知的人大多数都是不懂编程的，所以我也没办法让他们自建消息服务器。简单讨论之后我决定在我的服务器上搭建一个QQ机器人，直接将通知发送到群聊里面。</p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>需要Python环境，Windows和Linux均可。但因为要一直监听，所以还是得部署到Linux服务器上。</p></blockquote>\n<h1 id=\"搭建机器人环境\"><a href=\"#搭建机器人环境\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"搭建机器人环境\"></a>搭建机器人环境</h1><h2 id=\"命令行操作\"><a href=\"#命令行操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"命令行操作\"></a>命令行操作</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>下面的命令都在Ubuntu上执行。</p></blockquote>\n<p>首先要保证当前python的版本大于等于3.8，如果低于此版本则升级Python。<br><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684929926644-355358e4-a801-453b-9e9c-ea1b3ad87995.png#averageHue=%23343943&clientId=u6fd4872e-e490-4&from=paste&height=35&id=ub47ccb5a&originHeight=66&originWidth=680&originalType=binary&ratio=1.875&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=11497&status=done&style=none&taskId=ubce442a0-f438-463b-a35d-840a36020ce&title=&width=362.6666666666667\" alt=\"image.png\"><br>然后安装python虚拟环境和pipx：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">apt-get install python3-venv\npython3.8 -m pip install --user pipx\npython3.8 -m pipx ensurepath</code></pre>\n<p>关闭当前终端后重新打开，再执行：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">pipx install nb-cli</code></pre>\n<p><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684929497861-5ef9f9d8-ac2f-4c99-935e-f5b548ff1fe3.png#averageHue=%232e333c&clientId=u6fd4872e-e490-4&from=paste&height=91&id=u9f6f1917&originHeight=170&originWidth=1067&originalType=binary&ratio=1.875&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=24077&status=done&style=none&taskId=udf937447-2f45-4d2e-8f0a-94fdfee7a74&title=&width=569.0666666666667\" alt=\"image.png\"><br>接下来就就可以创建项目了：<code>nb create</code><br>选择的选项如下：<br><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684929592941-fdb189f0-6d58-46b7-a297-f9535967045e.png#averageHue=%232d323b&clientId=u6fd4872e-e490-4&from=paste&height=125&id=uab68a556&originHeight=235&originWidth=1369&originalType=binary&ratio=1.875&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=51541&status=done&style=none&taskId=uae9f51af-38fb-4775-8610-1be580c9a2b&title=&width=730.1333333333333\" alt=\"image.png\"><br><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684929616323-311ceed3-0f0b-4de0-a043-ac8269f2f593.png#averageHue=%232c313a&clientId=u6fd4872e-e490-4&from=paste&height=108&id=uc2605ab3&originHeight=202&originWidth=1359&originalType=binary&ratio=1.875&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=42520&status=done&style=none&taskId=ud5771b1b-4140-4282-8bb0-079e705a5f7&title=&width=724.8\" alt=\"image.png\"><br><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684929659662-b269c619-e033-474f-ae8b-27144d4d4baa.png#averageHue=%23323741&clientId=u6fd4872e-e490-4&from=paste&height=63&id=u878a634c&originHeight=118&originWidth=1184&originalType=binary&ratio=1.875&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=26905&status=done&style=none&taskId=u553c1d59-a520-42b9-9604-36a6f362bbf&title=&width=631.4666666666667\" alt=\"image.png\"><br><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684930051395-99721bc9-5d89-430f-990d-10eeb29e49ce.png#averageHue=%232e323b&clientId=u6fd4872e-e490-4&from=paste&height=59&id=ua898b28a&originHeight=110&originWidth=1354&originalType=binary&ratio=1.875&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=19820&status=done&style=none&taskId=uadfb7c04-f0c0-4c0f-8b1b-6d3c858daeb&title=&width=722.1333333333333\" alt=\"image.png\"><br>进入刚才创建的目录，安装<code>gocqhttp</code>插件。这是模拟实现的一个qq客户端：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\">nb plugin install nonebot-plugin-gocqhttp</code></pre>\n<p>最后<code>nb run</code>执行即可打开web面板：<br><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684930223249-711e9bbe-21c5-4941-999f-9ce546a03087.png#averageHue=%232f353f&clientId=u6fd4872e-e490-4&from=paste&height=311&id=uaea56083&originHeight=583&originWidth=1560&originalType=binary&ratio=1.875&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=168622&status=done&style=none&taskId=uf4451b8e-f288-45d7-a1d9-31e936de2e1&title=&width=832\" alt=\"image.png\"><br><strong>小技巧</strong>：这里用了vscode端口转发，所以无需到服务器提供商那里配置安全组。</p>\n<h2 id=\"管理面板操作\"><a href=\"#管理面板操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"管理面板操作\"></a>管理面板操作</h2><p>浏览器访问<code>http://127.0.0.1:8081/go-cqhttp/</code>，即可打开管理面板。<br><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684930349714-19ca831a-194b-4483-96ae-b868182841e4.png#averageHue=%23acb782&clientId=u6fd4872e-e490-4&from=paste&height=544&id=uda089fc4&originHeight=1020&originWidth=1887&originalType=binary&ratio=1.875&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=332520&status=done&style=none&taskId=ufe6248f9-38bc-4137-96d0-886677f2399&title=&width=1006.4\" alt=\"image.png\"><br>添加账号输入你想创建机器人的qq号的账号密码（建议开小号），设备我选择的是iPad。识别到账号后启动即可：<br><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684930667694-7e3c6e89-e729-4516-a3c4-a1931be81f3a.png#averageHue=%2379b673&clientId=u6fd4872e-e490-4&from=paste&height=509&id=ufeee4ceb&originHeight=954&originWidth=1875&originalType=binary&ratio=1.875&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=103318&status=done&style=none&taskId=u2a0f090a-1b7a-46ce-9c40-d0f06f2318e&title=&width=1000\" alt=\"image.png\"><br>注意上面可以输入选项：<br><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684930729864-59b01f7b-4cdc-48a6-b195-064bc5f4d95a.png#averageHue=%232b333b&clientId=u6fd4872e-e490-4&from=paste&height=404&id=u91afce6f&originHeight=757&originWidth=828&originalType=binary&ratio=1.875&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=162178&status=done&style=none&taskId=u8bcfedf8-f511-4971-984a-700b9100437&title=&width=441.6\" alt=\"image.png\"><br>登录成功：<br><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684931016821-e471fda5-8773-4dbb-89ac-bcb452583cec.png#averageHue=%232e3940&clientId=u6fd4872e-e490-4&from=paste&height=295&id=u024c0aa5&originHeight=553&originWidth=842&originalType=binary&ratio=1.875&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=155959&status=done&style=none&taskId=u252ac9e8-91b4-4d5f-b117-c7360d43e13&title=&width=449.06666666666666\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<h1 id=\"搭建后端\"><a href=\"#搭建后端\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"搭建后端\"></a>搭建后端</h1><h2 id=\"原理\"><a href=\"#原理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"原理\"></a>原理</h2><p>登录成功后，即可选择群聊或好友发送消息。<br>创建一个demo群，然后向这个群发送消息。点击发送后在群聊里面也能看到。<br><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684931232097-dfbcd225-cf63-44e8-8c50-7c49f5bdfc00.png#averageHue=%23f9f9f9&clientId=u6fd4872e-e490-4&from=paste&height=155&id=ud6bf033a&originHeight=290&originWidth=412&originalType=binary&ratio=1.875&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=12896&status=done&style=none&taskId=ua11695b8-1816-4bcf-a1d5-15ec07b84cb&title=&width=219.73333333333332\" alt=\"image.png\"><br>浏览器抓包结果：<br><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684931386409-5f3e77fd-3fa8-4a80-9772-7d5ba05d427d.png#averageHue=%23faf9f8&clientId=u6fd4872e-e490-4&from=paste&height=106&id=u539ee573&originHeight=198&originWidth=902&originalType=binary&ratio=1.875&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=22163&status=done&style=none&taskId=ua99275f6-3033-4953-8173-818cd9441bd&title=&width=481.06666666666666\" alt=\"image.png\"><br>查看post请求的data部分：<br><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684931328999-dc022a7f-8d9f-4df1-8e6b-9186111430b8.png#averageHue=%23faf8f7&clientId=u6fd4872e-e490-4&from=paste&height=105&id=uc50091a2&originHeight=197&originWidth=515&originalType=binary&ratio=1.875&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=19059&status=done&style=none&taskId=ue5f16280-4473-401d-bcde-90fb10a8f3a&title=&width=274.6666666666667\" alt=\"image.png\"><br>差不多可以明白了，<strong>只要向这个url发送post请求即可</strong>。现在使用<strong>postman</strong>模拟这个请求来验证想法：<br><img src=\"https://acg-api.fullcomb.top/proxy?url=https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2023/png/2648742/1684931515199-d66ec3c8-ee6b-4323-ab8c-7aac61d6f1a4.png#averageHue=%23fcfbfb&clientId=u6fd4872e-e490-4&from=paste&height=287&id=u476c08a1&originHeight=538&originWidth=1249&originalType=binary&ratio=1.875&rotation=0&showTitle=false&size=72494&status=done&style=none&taskId=u6e39d1a7-2b95-4cf1-ade0-f2f55079a14&title=&width=666.1333333333333\" alt=\"image.png\"><br>发送请求后，得到message的响应，然后也可以在QQ群里看到这个消息。<br>所以这就简单了啊，需要发送消息直接<code>requests.post</code>就行了。把这个post请求整合到代码里面就可以实现qq机器人发送群通知了。</p>\n<h2 id=\"实现\"><a href=\"#实现\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"实现\"></a>实现</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-python\" data-language=\"python\"><code class=\"language-python\">import requests\nimport json\n\nfor new in news:\n    data &#x3D; &#123;&quot;message&quot;: f&quot;@全体成员 积分商城上新✨\\n&#123;new[0]&#125;，&#123;new[1]&#125;&quot;, &quot;group_id&quot;: &quot;xxxxxx&quot;&#125;\n    header &#x3D; &#123;\n        &quot;Content-Type&quot;: &quot;application&#x2F;json&quot;\n    &#125;\n    data &#x3D; json.dumps(data)\n    res &#x3D; requests.post(&quot;http:&#x2F;&#x2F;127.0.0.1:8080&#x2F;go-cqhttp&#x2F;api&#x2F;xxxxxxx&#x2F;api?name&#x3D;send_msg&quot;, data, headers &#x3D; header)</code></pre>\n<p>总之就是这么简单。</p>\n","text":"之前有个一次性需要通知很多人的需求，而那些需要通知的人大多数都是不懂编程的，所以我也没办法让他们自建消息服务器。简单讨论之后我决定在我的服务器上搭建一个QQ机器人，直接将通知发送到群聊里面。 需要Python环境，Windows和Linux均可。但因为要一直监听，所以还是得部署到...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"1.4k","symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"分享","slug":"分享","count":11,"path":"api/categories/分享.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"python","slug":"python","count":14,"path":"api/tags/python.json"},{"name":"QQ机器人","slug":"QQ机器人","count":1,"path":"api/tags/QQ机器人.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E6%9C%BA%E5%99%A8%E4%BA%BA%E7%8E%AF%E5%A2%83\"><span class=\"toc-text\">搭建机器人环境</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4%E